::Feline::

She looked at him and blushed slightly."I hate to admit it, but yes. 
I'm lost. After you left, I just started walking around and have no 
idea how I got here."  She had her hands on her hips."So where did 
you run off to in such a hurry? Nothing bad I hope." she said with a 
slight chuckle. She took his arm and purred. "So how about that walk 
now......handsome." She smiled at him and looked into his eyes.
